{"tid":1993022,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"香港有冇可能出現一個係立法會打柒建制派既議員","createTime":"2020-04-28T13:10:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-08T10:12:38.000Z","uid":126889,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"6ee8da6e2b9ed846c03d58f371fd63701502070e","tid":1993022,"uid":126889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T13:10:38.000Z","msg":"如題"},{"pid":"aa8d641a79e409a0578a181a8749b3508caaf9bb","tid":1993022,"uid":2419,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T13:15:55.000Z","msg":"建你老母"},{"pid":"8d0300fccd0dc89ad3132780d4ec07a97eb8fcab","tid":1993022,"uid":126889,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"aa8d641a79e409a0578a181a8749b3508caaf9bb","tid":1993022,"uid":2419,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T13:15:55.000Z","msg":"建你老母"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T13:17:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />sorry"},{"pid":"b1971bd1a51aee558839414bff3bbf331e2e1e78","tid":1993022,"uid":89608,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T13:18:07.000Z","msg":"建制派打人就得, 仲會俾法官形容為高尚情操<br />\n民主派打建制, 會死得好慘"},{"pid":"fe52d878719ab42d893ba63ba38c6a6e795f3775","tid":1993022,"uid":52946,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T13:18:10.000Z","msg":"建乜撚野呀?又建制又反對派呀<br />\n保皇黨/亂港派/親中派/親共派/奶共派呀 屌你老母"},{"pid":"34da110996660252be084827185402d8cfd3c63d","tid":1993022,"uid":20867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T13:22:44.000Z","msg":"唔好意思，泛民reserve曬D議席la<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f23226c48a615af1d4f34c521990fbb2607bc3a","tid":1993022,"uid":282637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T13:23:56.000Z","msg":"朱高正姓朱,咁...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e59457c67db712f592daf497d9772acb65dc81b5","tid":1993022,"uid":126889,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"9f23226c48a615af1d4f34c521990fbb2607bc3a","tid":1993022,"uid":282637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T13:23:56.000Z","msg":"朱高正姓朱,咁...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T13:28:45.000Z","msg":"真正制度內抗爭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50d131d9627cd267bed4aeb61cfd53b292151fb2","tid":1993022,"uid":126889,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T13:31:19.000Z","msg":"// 有關議員因犯罪被判監禁而喪失資格，立法會和區議會有不同的規定。根據《區議會條例》，任何民選區議員如果在當選後被裁定犯罪，並判處3個月以上的監禁，即喪失議員資格，不論是否獲得緩刑。對於立法會議員，並沒有同樣的規定：按《立法會條例》，任何人如果被裁定犯罪，並就所犯罪行被判處3個月以上的監禁，則在被定罪後的5年內，他喪失在立法會選舉中獲提名為候選人及當選為議員的資格。可是，如果已在任的立法會議員犯罪被判監禁，不論刑期長短，他並不會馬上喪失議席；他的議員資格須按《基本法》第七十九條(六)處理，即除了被判犯有刑事罪行、判處監禁一個月以上之外，並要經立法會出席會議的議員三分之二通過解除其職務，然後才由立法會主席宣告其喪失立法會議員的資格。<br />\n<br />\n立法會議員被判處監禁後，議會就要否解除其職務進行辯論，以往曾發生過不止一次。其中有因為解除職務的議案獲三分之二議員通過，被判監禁的議員便喪失議席；也有因為議案未獲得三分之二議員支持，有關議員得保留議席。//<br />\n<br />\nsource (老鼠曾) <a href=\"https://www.thinkhk.com/article/2019-04/18/34070.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thinkhk.com%2Farticle%2F2019-04%2F18%2F34070.html&d=C0QxMr2ftqWfBh1dRblImJUrr29XULmfQ5XcAAvzh4c%3D&h=e79e4b52\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thinkhk.com/article/2019-04/18/34070.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔洗35+ 23+就得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e6fabda0b09be48a0da8b4546567c304f6043a8","tid":1993022,"uid":229502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9f23226c48a615af1d4f34c521990fbb2607bc3a","tid":1993022,"uid":282637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T13:23:56.000Z","msg":"朱高正姓朱,咁...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T13:32:49.000Z","msg":"反共復明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e198333636f58486e1d1fb28d7ce17cebb1632dd","tid":1993022,"uid":282637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T16:35:58.000Z","msg":"(YOUTUBE戰線)(香港電台92.8萬 位訂閱者)同我訂閱港台,要過百萬<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1992439\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1992439</a>"},{"pid":"55b9ed2e493513a6097eb67256a61e7d736494ff","tid":1993022,"uid":126889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T10:00:31.000Z","msg":"再推一下先 應下景"},{"pid":"cf624af2c2379094c1982554bf183d5afe777bf2","tid":1993022,"uid":126889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T10:06:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d6fe76e9e69115cc5aa140c0fbac04574927f45","tid":1993022,"uid":230104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T10:07:37.000Z","msg":"立法會附近呢？"},{"pid":"65a9c08d512d4a24e74af91bcf8aab2fdc898b1f","tid":1993022,"uid":112622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T10:09:37.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"64a406e0af67008764e04a178c45fd9b1800df65","tid":1993022,"uid":126889,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T10:12:38.000Z","msg":"第一個打柒建制派既議員 我一世既票都投比佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}